results.name: Positions of non-crossing fixed-point-free involutions encoded by A014486 in A055089. Permutation of A064640.
maple: NonCrossingTransposAux := proc(s,ii) local e,p,i,j; i := ii; p := []; for e in s do p := permul(p,NonCrossingTransposAux(e,i+1)); j := i+CountParens(e)+1; p := permul(p,[[i,j]]); i := j+1; od; RETURN(p); end;
CountParens := proc(s) local e,k; if(0 = nops(s)) then RETURN(0); fi; e := 0; for k in s do e := e+2+CountParens(k); od; RETURN(e); end;
xref: Maple procedure binexp2pars given in A057501, permul in A060125.
